### Start Custom Saga
POST http://localhost:5000/api/saga/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flowName": "user-registration-flow",
  "initialData": {
    "userId": "custom-user-001",
    "email": "custom@example.com",
    "username": "customuser",
    "registrationSource": "web"
  }
}

